dal_main_3617506\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 26, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104zwr1665702640525.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zwr1665702640525.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zwr1665702640525.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"zwr1665702640525\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Multiple Rows\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This widget property determines whether tabs are distributed over multiple rows if the width of all tabs together exceeds the width of the tab widget. <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code> (default).\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zwr1665702640525__p_d105950e1_d105951e1_d105952e1\">TabEx: <code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>Multiline<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code></p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zwr1665702640525__p_d105953e1_d105954e1_d105955e1\">Tab: <code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>Multi<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code></p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zwr1665702640525__section_bfd_ncd_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1153508e89\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"zwr1665702640525__table_d11987e1_d11988e1_d11989e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dynamic?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Yes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Supported in Grid?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dependencies:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">None</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zwr1665702640525__section_kp5_pcd_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1153508e135\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zwr1665702640525__p_d105962e1_d105963e1_d105964e1\">By default, the tab strip is a single line that\n        occupies the width of the widget. If the number of tabs exceeds the display area of the\n        strip, scroll buttons are added the tab strip, enabling the user to scroll to the unseen\n        tabs.</p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"zwr1665702640525__fig_d105965e1_d105966e1_d105967e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>Tab Strip as Single Row, with Scroll Buttons</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zwr1665702640525__p_d105971e1_d105972e1_d105973e1\"><img alt=\"Image\" class=\"image\" id=\"zwr1665702640525__image_uqy_wcd_zwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/tabstrip_single.png?_LANG=enus\"/>When <code class=\"ph codeph\">true</code>, the widget displays the tab strip with multiple\n        rows.</p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"zwr1665702640525__fig_d105974e1_d105975e1_d105976e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 2. </span>Tab Strip with Multiple Rows</figcaption>\n<img alt=\"Image\" class=\"image\" id=\"zwr1665702640525__image_ztn_ycd_zwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/tabstrip_multiple.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zwr1665702640525__section_dwt_zcd_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1153508e173\">Example: Using in ProcScript</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zwr1665702640525__p_d105983e1_d105984e1_d105985e1\">You can use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$properties</span> or\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldproperties</span> to set or get the property and its value. For more\n        information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zie1665702558978.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zie1665702558978.html\" title=\"Return or set the current widget properties of a field.\">$properties</a> and <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aud1705998763272.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aud1705998763272.html\" title=\"Return or set the current widget properties of an instance of a field.\">$fieldproperties</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"zwr1665702640525__pre_a2w_1dd_zwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(TAB)=\"multiline=true\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zwr1665702640525__section_if1_bdd_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1153508e206\">Applies to</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"zwr1665702640525__ul_fdn_2dd_zwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zwr1665702640525__li_d41645e1_d41646e1_d41647e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zwr1665702640525__p_d103784e1_d103785e1_d103786e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bzj1665702641924.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bzj1665702641924.html\" title=\"The utab widget enables users to navigate through a collection of contained forms by clicking a tab to display the form. Uniface provides a logical widget called Tab, which is mapped to utab.\">utab (Tab)</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zwr1665702640525__li_d41648e1_d41649e1_d41650e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zwr1665702640525__p_d103787e1_d103788e1_d103789e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gyf1688451219719.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gyf1688451219719.html\" title=\"The utabex widget enables users to navigate through a collection of contained forms by clicking a tab to display the form. The utabex widget is highly customizable, allowing extensive control over the appearance and behavior of the tabs. Uniface provides a logical widget called TabEx, which is mapped to utabex.\">utabex (TabEx)</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617506\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617506\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Multiple Rows Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Multiple Rows This widget property determines whether tabs are distributed over multiple rows if the width of all tabs together exceeds the width of the tab widget. True or False (default). TabEx: \" Multiline = True | False \" Tab: \" Multi = True | False \" Usage Dynamic? Yes Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: None Description By default, the tab strip is a single line that occupies the width of the widget. If the number of tabs exceeds the display area of the strip, scroll buttons are added the tab strip, enabling the user to scroll to the unseen tabs. Figure 1. Tab Strip as Single Row, with Scroll Buttons When true , the widget displays the tab strip with multiple rows. Figure 2. Tab Strip with Multiple Rows Example: Using in ProcScript You can use $properties or $fieldproperties to set or get the property and its value. For more information, see $properties and $fieldproperties . $fieldproperties(TAB)=\"multiline=true\" Copy Applies to utab (Tab) utabex (TabEx) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}